flowchart TD
  A[Trigger: Initiation of an NPI program milestone or formal EOL review window (e.g., program start, 6-month ramp review, or executive EOL decision cadence).]
  A --> N1[Stream: DDM/Crawlers + STREAMS - Ingest program, BOM, inventory, demand, supplier data]
  N1 --> N2[Cortex: Subject Areas + Data Quality & Validation - Assemble subject area and validate constraints]
  N2 --> N3[Cortex: Remote Functions (optimization solver) invoked by Process Builder - Run deterministic optimizer to generate phased EOL options]
  N3 --> N4{PB: Process (Process Builder) + CWB Lifecycle - Route recommended plan to stakeholders for approval}
  N4 -->|Primary| N5[PB: Remote Functions (SAP writeback) + Notification - Execute approved plan and notify systems/partners]
  N5 --> N6[UI: UI Screen (dashboard) + Cortex Monitoring - Surface results and monitor KPIs]
  N6 --> Z1[Outcome: Optimized phase-out schedule that minimizes inventory write-downs and COGS, maintains target OTIF during ramp-down, reduces working capital tied to obsolete parts, and aligns supplier commitments with phased production reductions.]
  N4 -->|Optimizer returns infeasible solution...| B1[Process Builder triggers alternative solver run with relaxed constraints and flags affected suppliers; create exception CWB routing to procurement and engineering]
  B1 --> O1[Outcome: Feasible contingency schedule proposed; procurement engages suppliers for capacity negotiation or rework options.]
  O1 --> End[End]
  N4 -->|Stakeholder rejects recommended plan ...| B2[Capture override inputs via CWB Lifecycle, run targeted what-if Remote Function to show impact of requested changes, and re-submit for approval]
  B2 --> O2[Outcome: Adjusted plan reflecting stakeholder constraints with quantified trade-offs; approval or escalation path recorded.]
  O2 --> End[End]
  N4 -->|Significant supplier non-compliance a...| B3[Process Builder branches to Agent Team (Procurement) with packaged exception details and suggested mitigation actions; re-run optimizer with updated supplier status]
  B3 --> O3[Outcome: Rapid mitigation (alternate sourcing, slowed phase-out, or temporary buffer allocation) and updated plan written back to SAP.]
  O3 --> End[End]
  Z1 --> End[End]